 103:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****     (+) To read the RTC TimeStamp Time and Date register, use the HAL_RTCEx_GetTimeStamp()
 104:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****         function.
