 108:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   [..]
 109:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****     (+) Enable the RTC internal TimeStamp using the HAL_RTCEx_SetInternalTimeStamp() function.
 110:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****         User has to check internal timestamp occurrence using __HAL_RTC_INTERNAL_TIMESTAMP_GET_FLAG
 111:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****     (+) To read the RTC TimeStamp Time and Date register, use the HAL_RTCEx_GetTimeStamp()
 112:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****         function.
