 132:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****      (+) To write to the RTC Backup Data registers, use the HAL_RTCEx_BKUPWrite()
 133:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****          function.
 134:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****      (+) To read the RTC Backup registers, use the HAL_RTCEx_BKUPRead()
 135:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****          function.
 136:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****      (+) To reset the RTC Backup registers and erase the device secrets,
 137:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****          use HAL_RTCEx_BKUPErase() function.
 138:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****      (+) Enable the lock of the Boot hardware Key using the HAL_RTCEx_LockBootHardwareKey()
 139:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****          function.
 140:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****          The backup registers from TAMP_BKP0R to TAMP_BKP7R cannot be accessed neither in
 141:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****          read nor in write (they are read as 0 and write ignore).
 142:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****      (+) Configure the erase of the Device Secrets using HAL_RTCEx_ConfigEraseDeviceSecrets()
