1530:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****                          ##### Tamper functions #####
1531:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   ==============================================================================
1532:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   [..]
1533:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****    (+) Before calling any tamper or internal tamper function, you have to call first
1534:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****        HAL_RTC_Init() function.
1535:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****    (+) In that one you can select to output tamper event on RTC pin.
1536:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   [..]
1537:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****    (+) Enable the Tamper and configure the Tamper filter count, trigger Edge
1538:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****        or Level according to the Tamper filter (if equal to 0 Edge else Level)
1539:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****        value, sampling frequency, NoErase, MaskFlag, precharge or discharge and
1540:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****        Pull-UP, timestamp using the HAL_RTCEx_SetTamper() function.
1541:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****        You can configure Tamper with interrupt mode using HAL_RTCEx_SetTamper_IT() function.
1542:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****    (+) The default configuration of the Tamper erases the backup registers. To avoid
1543:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****        erase, enable the NoErase field on the TAMP_TAMPCR register.
1544:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   [..]
1545:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****    (+) Enable Internal Tamper and configure it with interrupt, timestamp using
1546:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****        the HAL_RTCEx_SetInternalTamper() function.
1547:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c **** 
1548:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rtc_ex.c **** @endverbatim
